oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Collection of buttons, bullets, and other implements
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This grouping of dug relics includes several different varieties of minie balls, a US cartridge box breast strap plate, the back section of a US waist belt plate, a cartridge casing, and the reed from a harmonica. All items were found along Tellico Ave. in Athens, Tennessee.
